                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150510-51-defend548 t18150510-51-punish310"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ALLEN, <rs id="t18150510-51-verdict311" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150510-51-verdict311" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
